              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">天狗咒雷·雷礫</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/2185a287c1725779bdfe00b0fe84353e_7290179871524133811.png",
