                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "煌煌千道鎮式"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，我方出戰角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">鳴煌護持</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">鳴煌護持</span></strong></p><p>所附屬角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">元素戰技</span>和<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">元素爆發</span>造成的傷害+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_52314326775351430.png",
                "id": "talent98060",
                "key": "天狗咒雷·伏",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/1ce18b0d1d4b2b162276892a85feea79_851032029288634508.png",
                "title": "天狗咒雷·伏"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，我方出戰角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">鳴煌護持</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">鳴煌護持</span></strong></p><p>所附屬角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">元素戰技</span>和<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">元素爆發</span>造成的傷害+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2555353814546086777.png",
                "id": "talent28353",
                "key": "天狗咒雷·雷礫",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/7a1026e18244fc72af3873f6a6dc44ab_8596687725292602329.png",
                "title": "天狗咒雷·雷礫"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span>」</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_4178982104005127261.png",
                "id": "talent88664",
                "key": "雷元素傷害",
